dc_description_s: This dataset contains fourteen (14) registered 3D laser scans of Glenbow General Store and Post Office on 19th July 2017 for documentation purposes. The scans were collected with Z+F 5010X scanner and processed with Z+F Laser Control v.8.9.0.
